Etymology. The specific name of the new species,
ramirezi
, is devoted to Claudio C. Ramírez Rivera. (associate professor of the University of Talca, Chile ), who is coauthor of several papers on Chilean
Neuquenaphis
species (
Quiroz et al ., 1999
;
Blackman et al. , 2003
;
Gaete-Eastman et al ., 2004
